qual to (x) if paid by such Lender, the overnight Federal Funds Effective Rate or (y) if paid by such Borrower, the then applicable rate of interest, calculated in accordance with Section 2.12, for the respective Loans (but without any requirement to pay any amounts in respect thereof pursuant to Section 3.02).
