t deem necessary or appropriate in connection with the foregoing. The release of the Collateral pursuant to this Section shall not be effective until the date (the "") that (i) the Collateral Agent has filed all termination statements and releases, deemed necessary or appropriate by the Company, which the Collateral Agent shall promptly do upon satisfaction by the Company of the conditions set forth in this
