Section 7.01 . Neither the Company nor any of its Subsidiaries will engage in any business if, as a result, the general nature of the business, taken on a consolidated basis, which would then be engaged in by the Company and its Subsidiaries, would be substantially changed from the general nature of the business engaged in by the Company and its Subsidiaries on the Closing Date.
