Section 1.02. .
Incorporation by Reference of Trust Indenture Act
Whenever this Supplemental Indenture refers to a provision of the TIA, the portion of such provision required to be incorporated herein in order for this Supplemental Indenture to be qualified under the TIA is incorporated by reference in and made a part of this Supplemental Indenture. The following TIA terms used in this Supplemental Indenture have the following meanings:
"" means the Notes.
indenture securities
