Ladies and Gentlemen:
We are acting as counsel for American Greetings Corporation, an Ohio corporation (the ""), in connection with the issuance and sale of $225,000,000 aggregate principal amount of 7.375% Senior Notes due 2021 of the Company (the ""), pursuant to the Underwriting Agreement, dated November 16, 2011 (the ""), entered into by and between the Company and J.P. Morgan Securities LLC, acting as representative of the several underwriters named therein (collectively, the ""). The Notes will be issued pursuant to an indenture (the "") to be entered into between the Company and The Bank of Nova Scotia Trust Company of New York, as trustee (the ""), as amended and supplemented by a supplemental indenture (the "") to be entered into between the Company and the Trustee (the Base Indenture, as so amended and supplemented by the Supplemental Indenture, the "").
