14.1 The Sellers and the Purchaser intend that the sale and purchase of the Business and the Business Assets hereunder shall be treated, for VAT purposes, as neither a supply of goods nor a supply of services pursuant to the provisions of section 49 VATA and Article 5 () of the Value Added Tax (Special Provisions) Order 1995 (sc 1995/1268) and the parties agree to use reasonable endeavours to ensure that it is so treated.
